YY主播伴侣-YY Live Assistant Privacy Policy

Effective date: June 2, 2026

We value your privacy and data security. This policy explains how YY Live Companion handles your information.

1. Information We Collect
You may enter fan nicknames, levels, tags, interactions, scripts, flow steps, schedules, settings, and VIP status. This data is used to provide in-app management, reminders, and display.

2. Storage
The current version mainly stores data locally on your device, including fan, script, flow, schedule, settings, and VIP data. We do not actively upload this local data to a server.

3. Permissions
Notifications and audio playback, if used, are only for schedule reminders, flow reminders, and background music playback.

4. VIP Subscription Information
If App Store in-app subscriptions are used, purchases, trials, renewals, and refunds are processed by Apple. The app may use Apple subscription status to unlock VIP features. We do not directly access sensitive payment information.

5. Third-Party Services
Current third-party components mainly support basic UI layout. If cloud sync, analytics, crash reporting, or payment validation is added, this policy will explain the usage.

6. Data Use
Your data is used to provide fan management, tag management, scripts, flow reminders, schedule reminders, music playback, settings, and VIP unlocking.

7. Security
We make reasonable efforts to protect your data. Because local data depends on your device, please protect your device, account, and backups.

8. Your Rights
You can add, edit, and delete data in the app, or remove stored data by deleting the app or clearing local data.

9. Minors
Minors should use the app and membership services under guardian guidance.

10. Contact
For privacy questions, contact us through in-app feedback or the app store contact channel.
